quran[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa. …óeen ko aayeeje deftere e janngeteende …ďannginnde."
  15,2,"Na waawi heefer…ďe …ďen njeloyto sinno …ďe laatino juul…ďe."
  15,3,"Accu …ďe, …ďe √Īaama …ďe dakmitoo, yela soklina …ďe; arma …ďe nganndoya."
  15,4,"Min kalkaani saare woo, si wanaa hara no woodani nde happu ganndaa…óo."
  15,5,"Mofte woo adotaako lajal mun, …ďe nee…ďnantaake kadi."
  15,6,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Ko aan yo mo deftere nden jippinaa e mun, an ko a peetu…óo."
  15,7,"Ko ha…óno addanaa men maleyikaaji si a laatike gooŇč…óu…óo?"""
  15,8,"Min njippinirtaa maleykaaji si wonaa fii goonga; …ďe wonataa ontuma, nee…ďnantee…ďe."
  15,9,"Minen min njippinii deftere nden, minen kadi ko min reenoo…ďe nde."
  15,10,"GooŇč…óii min nuliino ado maa, e le∆ī∆īi adinoo…ďe."
  15,11,"Nulaa…óo (woo) araani e ma…ď…ďe si wonaa …ďe njalkitay mo."
  15,12,"Ko wano nii min naadiri …óum e …ďer…óe bon…ďe …ďeen."
  15,13,"∆Āe ngooŇč…óintaa nde, gooŇč…óii sunna aram…ďe …ďen yawtiino."
  15,14,"Hay si minn udditanno …ďe damal ka kammu, …ďe mba…ótini hi…ďe ∆īawra heen."
  15,15,"…ďe mbi'ayno: ""nganndee gite amen …óeen kippa. Wurin ko min yim…ďe wilaa…ďe""."
  15,16,"GooŇč…óii min mba…óii ka kammu koode, min cu…óirani …óe ndaaroo…ďe."
  15,17,"Min ndeeni mbo e kala seytaane diiwaa…óo."
  15,18,"Si wonaa oon guujju…óo nan…óe, o jokkintina hoodere-fi…óaynnde jal…ďunde."
  15,19,"Leydi ndin, min weerti ndi min werlii e mayri pelle, min puu…óini e mayri kala huunde e…ď…ďaande."
  15,20,"Min mba…óani on e mayri wuurir…óe, e …ďeen …ďe on laatanooki arsikoo…ďe …óum."
  15,21,"Huunde alaa si wanaa marga mun ko ka amen, min njippintaa …óuum si wanaa e e…ď…ďoore anndaande."
  15,22,"Min ngurti keneeli …óiin hawrondirooji e duule; min njippiniri ka kammu ndiyam min njarniri on …óaam, wonaa onon mari …óam."
  15,23,"Ko minen kadi ngoni ko wuurnata min mbara, ko minen ngoni ronoo…ďe …ďeen."
  15,24,"GooŇč…óii min nganndii adii…ďe e mon …ďen GooŇč…óii min nganndii sakkitii…ďe …ďen."
  15,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko KaŇčko moo…ďoyta …ďe. KaŇčko ko o √Īee√Īo, ganndu…óo."
  15,26,"GooŇč…óii min tagii ne…ó…óaŇčke on e sen∆īayngal, e (cenlatngal) loopal-…ďalewal …ďowrungal."
  15,27,"E jinnaaji …óin, min tagiri ndu ko adii, e yiite ooyunge."
  15,28,"JaŇčto tuma nde Joomi maa daalannoo maleykaji'en: ""min ko Mi tagiroowo …ďanndiŇčke immorde e sen∆īayngal, e loopal-…ďalewal …ďowrungal"
  15,29,"si mi fotndiii mo, mi wuttii e makko ruuhu am on, haray suuyanee mo ko on sujju…ďe""."
  15,30,"Maleykajien fof cujji …ďe denndaangal."
  15,31,"si wonaa ibliisa, o salii tawdeede e sujjoo…ďe …ďen."
  15,32,"O daali: ""eey ma ibliisa, e ko he…ď maa a laatodaaki e sujju…ďe …ďeen?"""
  15,33,"O wi'i: ""mi wonatah sujjanoowo …ďanndinke mo tagu…óaa immorde e sen∆īayngal, e loopal-…ďalewal …ďowrungal""."
  15,34,"O daali: ""Yaltu toon, aan o ko a diiwaa…óo,"
  15,35,"pellet, kuddi fawike e ma haa √Īande njo…ďdi diina""."
  15,36,"O wi'i : ""joomi am, nee…ďnitanam haa √Īande nde…ďe immintintee""."
  15,37,"O daali:""Aa,ko a jeyaa…óo e nee…ďnitantee…ďe …ďen."
  15,38,"haa e √Īalaande happu ganndaa…óo""."
  15,39,"O wi'i: ""Joomi am, sabu ko mbewnu…óaa mi kon, ma mi cu…óinan …ďe ka leydi, ma mi bewnu …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe,"
  15,40,"si wanaa jeyaa…ďe maa, la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe""."
  15,41,"O daali: ""nogol …óoo ko laawol ka am poocciingol."
  15,42,"Pellet, jeyaa…ďe am …ďen, a alanaa …ďe cemmbe, si wonaa …ďeen bew…ďe jokku…ďe ma."
  15,43,"Pellet Jahannama on wonii fodoore ma…ď…ďe …ďe fof."
  15,44,"Henge mari dame jee…ói…ói; damal kala e majje no mari ge…óal senndaangal."
  15,45,"Pellet, gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen wonii e aljannaaji e …ďulli."
  15,46,"""Naatiree …ói e kisial, ko on hoolii…ďe""."
  15,47,"Min …óoofi kala ko woni e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe e konnaagu(cokotaagal): …ďe ngonti musi…ó…ďe fewtondir…ďe e dan…óe."
  15,48,"Tampere he…ďataa …ďe toon,, …ďe ngonah kadi yaltintee …ďe toon."
  15,49,"Yeetito jeyaa…ďe am …ďen, ko miin woni jaafotoo…óo, jurmtoo…óo On"
  15,50,"e wonnde lepte am …óeen, ko …óen ngoni lepte muus…óe …óen."
  15,51,"ha…ďru …ďe kadi fii ho…ď…ďe Ibraahiima …ďeen,"
  15,52,"Tuma …ďe naatunoo ka makko …ďe mbi'i: ""Salaam (Kisiyee mon)"". O maaki: ""minen ko min …óen∆īii …ďe on""."
  15,53,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Wota a faay, minen mi…óen mbeltinirma […ďi…ó…óo] gorko ganndo""."
  15,54,"O maaki: ""E on mbeltiniratkam […óuum] e hoore ko mi naywi ko? E ko mbeltinirton mi?"""
  15,55,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""min mbeltininirii ma goonga, wota a jeye e ta∆īii…ďe …ďeen""."
  15,56,"O maaki: ""Ko hommbo ta∆īotoo e yurmeende Joomi mun nden, si wonaa majju…ďe …ďeen?"""
  15,57,"O maaki: ""Ko woni fii mon, onon …ďee imminaa…ďe?""(nulee…ďe.)"
  15,58,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""minen min nulaa ko e yim…ďe bon…ďe,"
  15,59,"si wonaa …ďeynguure Luuti nde, pellet ko min da…óndoo…ďe …ďe denndaangal,"
  15,60,"si wonaa debbo makko on"". min koddirii oon …óon ko jeyaa…óo e halketee…ďe …ďen."
  15,61,"Nde imminaa…ďe …ďen ngaruno ka …ďeynguure Luuti,"
  15,62,"O maaki: ""onon ko on yim…ďe faaytaa …ďe""."
  15,63,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Wurin min ngaddanii ma ko …ďe ngonnoo e sikkitaade kon."
  15,64,"Min ngaddanii ma goonga kan, pellet ko min goonŇč…óu…ďe."
  15,65,"Yahdu e …ďeynguure maa ndeen ka ta∆īitannde jem- ma, jokkaa …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe; hara gooto e mo'on ye∆ī∆īitaaki, ndewon ka njamira…óon""."
  15,66,"Min anndini mo on fiyaaku: wonn¬īde wattannde …ďee …óoo, ko ta∆īetee…óum ka subaka."
  15,67,"Yim…ďe saare nden ngri he…ďe mbeltoro."
  15,68,"O maaki: ""…ďee …óoo ko ho…ď…ďe am, wata on wirtam.(cuhritam)."
  15,69,"Kulee Alla, wota on koynam""."
  15,70,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""e min ka…óaali ma [weernugol] tagoore nden?"""
  15,71,"O maaki: ""…ďee …óoo ko jiw…ďe am, si wonii ko on wa…óoo…ďe [go…ó…óum]!"""
  15,72,"Mi woondirii nguurndam maa! …ďe ngonii e siwrugol ma…ď…ďe he…ďe mbeemi."
  15,73,"Haacaango ngoon nanngiri …ďe ka pu…óal,"
  15,74,"Min mb…ótiniri dow mayre on ley mayre, min saa∆īini(to…ďri) e ma…ď…ďe kaa∆īe iwru…óe e loope ju…óaa…óe."
  15,75,"Wonii e …óuum, maandeeji wonan¬īde …ďen teskotoo…ďe."
  15,76,"Pellet, …óeen [ca'e] no e jurol(bolol) √Īii…ďngol."
  15,77,"Wonii e …óuum, maande wonan¬īde …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  15,78,"GooŇč…óii yim…ďe fitaare(sutu) …ďeen [kadi] ko too√Ī…ďe."
  15,79,"Min yo…ďtii e ma…ď…ďe. Pellet …óeen [ca'e] …ói…ói ngonii e laawol …ďanngungol."
  15,80,"GooŇč…ói yim…ďe (aynde) Hijiri nden njeddii nulaa…ďe …ďeen."
  15,81,"Min ngaddani …ďe aayeeje amen …óen, …ďe laatii …óuurnii…ďe …óe."
  15,82,"Hari he…ďe lesoynoo e pelle …óeen cuu…ói, ko …ďe hoolii…ďe."
  15,83,"Haacaango ngoon nanngi …ďe ka subaka."
  15,84,"Nafaani…ďe …óuum ko …ďe laatinoo he…ďe paggitoo."
  15,85,"Min tagiraani kammuuli …óiin e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, si wonaa e goonga. Pellet, darngal ngal ko arayngal! yaafora jaafaggol labaangol."
  15,86,"Tabitii ko Joomi maa woni Tak…óo, ganndu…óo."
  15,87,"GooŇč…óii min okkii ma jee…ói…ói ummorde …óimmitaa-ngol, e Alqur'aanaare mawnde nden."
  15,88,"Wata a …ďamtu gite maa …óen e neemaaji …ói lin dakmiti …ďe e mum en, wata a sunu e ma…ď…ďe, les…óin becce maa …óen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  15,89,"Maaku: ""min ko mi jertinoowo …ďannginoowo""."
  15,90,"Wano min njppinirnoo e senndoo…ďe [defte Alla] …ďen [lepte],"
  15,91,"∆Āeen wa…ó…ďe Alqur'aanaare nden ge…óe-ge…óe."
  15,92,"Mi woo…óndirii Joomi maa! Ma min la…ďndoyo …ďe fof ma…ď…ďe."
  15,93,"fii ko …ďe ngonnoo e huuwude.(gollude)."
  15,94,"Fe√Ī√Īin ko njamira-…óaa kon, …óuurno-…óaa sirkoo…ďe …ďeen."
  15,95,"minen min njonii ma e …ďen jalkitoo…ďe."
  15,96,"∆Āeen wa…ódoo…ďe e Alla dewetee…óo goo. arma ka …ďe ngannda."
  15,97,"GooŇč…óii mi…óen nganndi won¬īde bernde maa nde na …ďi…ótora ko …ďe kaalata kon."
  15,98,"Subbhinor yettugol Joomi maa, laato-daa e sujjoo…ďe …ďee."
  15,99,"ndewaa Joomi haa yananeede (maayde) ara e maa."
